Title: PLSS Florence County, WI 2019
Description: This data represents Public Land Survey System (PLSS) corners for Florence County, Wisconsin in 2019.[Data created using field gathered data and information provided through Florence County, Wisconsin Register of Deeds research.Direct Observation points were created from actual survey point data or from coordinates listed on recorded Certified Survey Maps (CSM).Calculated points were established by bearings and distances shown on numerous CSMs when tied to known corner locations.]

Title: PLSS Vilas County, WI 2018
Description: This data layer represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Vilas County, Wisconsin in 2018. [The current control point on the surface of the earth and its associated current coordinate value, generally determined by a surveying process and used to define an extremity of a boundary.]
Originator: Vilas County Land Information and Mapping Department
